<%# locals: (workspaces:, current_workspace:) -%>
<%# Desktop workspace-sidebar wrapper — provides the <aside> landmark
    and the boxed sidebar visual chrome. Contents (switcher + workspace
    nav items) live in _workspace_sidebar_items.html.erb, which is also
    rendered directly into the mobile-accordion content_for slot
    WITHOUT this chrome so the sidebar contents flow inline rather than
    as a nested sidebar.

    Mirrors the agent_os Notion/Linear pattern: switcher at top,
    workspace nav in the middle, settings link at bottom (Path Y Phase B).
    The Settings hub has its own sidebar (_settings_sidebar) with
    destination-specific nav items. -%>
<aside aria-label="<%= t("workspaces.sidebar.aria_label") %>"
       class="w-64 shrink-0 px-4 py-6 border-r border-border bg-surface">
  <%= render "shared/workspace_sidebar_items",
        workspaces: workspaces,
        current_workspace: current_workspace %>
</aside>
